lines: reg bya'i skye mched dang lnga yod pa'i phyir
gzugs kyi skye mched kyi mtshan nyid yod de
mig shes kyi bzung bya de yin pa'i phyir
gzugs kyi skye mched la dbye na gnyis yod de
dbyibs dang kha dog gnyis yod pa'i phyir
'chad par byed pa la mdzod las
rnam smin rgyu ni mi dge dang
dge ba zag bcas rnams kho na
zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir
'chad par byed pa la mdzod las
mtshungs ldan rgyu ni sems dag dang
sems byung rten mtshungs can rnams so
zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir
'chad par byed pa la mdzod las
kun 'gro zhes bya nyon mongs can
zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir
rtsa bar 'dod mi nus te
rnam smin gyi rgyu yin pa'i phyir
'chad par byed pa la mdzod las
rnam smin rgyu ni mi dge dang
dge ba zag bcas rnams kho na
zhes gsungs pa yin pa'i phyir
rtsa bar 'dod mi nus te
lung ma bstan yin pa'i phyir
rab yangs blo gros mkha' la shes bya'i tshon
ma 'dres dbang po'i gzhu bzhin rab bkra zhing
rnam dag rigs pa'i 'od 'bum cher spro ba
rigs pa'i dbang phyug phyogs glang grags pa rgyal
thub dbang bstan la thub dbang gnyis pa bzhin
bshad sgrub gling bzhi gsal ba'i nyi ma mchog
blo bzang rgyal ba gnyis pa sras bcas dang
'jam dbyangs bzhad pa'i rdo rje yab sras rgyal
rigs gzhung chu gter che la sa legs thon cing
dri med rigs pa'i 'od dkar zegs ma can
mtshon nas thar lam mig 'byed rjes su dran
gang 'di par du bskrun pa'i rnam dkar mthus
bstan pa'i spyin bdag dbang phyug zhir gshegs pa
mi khom gnas spangs rten mchog legs brgyud de
sa lam 'grod pa myur du mthar phyin shog
bstan la lhag bsam dge ba'i bdag mo che
er be sha ra sras bcas zhabs brten cing
phun tshogs bde sgyid dpal la rtag spyod dang
don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i bkra shis shog
phyag mdzod dka' chen blo bzang chos skyongs dang
yig mkhan dge slong blo bzang don 'grub ste
par rkod dge slong ngag dbang chos 'phel dang
dge slong dag dbang tshul khrims la sogs pa
gnas skabs bar chad kun zhi bsam don 'grub
mthar thug byang chen gegs med myur 'grub shog
bslu med bla ma yid ma mchog gsum mthus
bstan bsrung dba' bo mkhas 'gro'i 'phrin las dang
rten 'brel mi bslu chos nyid bden pa yis
ji ltar smon pa bshin du 'grub pa dang
'gro rnams 'tshe bral bstan pa'i bar bzung nas
theg mchog bshes dang rnam yang mi 'bral zhing
lhag bsam khyogs la ma rnams kun blang ste
bla med bdud bral bstan pa'i khur bzung nas
bshad sgrub bstan pa nyi ltar gsal gyur cig
bdag cag deng nas tshe rabs thams cad du
theg mchog bshes dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing
lhag bsam khyogs lam rnams kun blang ste
bla med bdud rtsis myur du ngoms gyur cig
dpal ldan stobs bcu mnga' pa'i bkra shis shog
bshad sgrub bstan pa rgyas pa'i brka shis shog
mi mthun g.yul las rgyal ba'i bkra shis shog
phun tshogs dpal la rol pa'i bkra shis shog
de la kun mkhyen bskal don yin pa'i phyir
sangs rgyas kun dngos rgyal dbang tsong kha pa'i
mdo rgyud mnga' bdag 'jam bzhad rdo rje'i gzhung
kun mkhyen dbang po ngag dbang bkra shis dpal
'jam dbyangs bla ma'i gsung gi bdud rtse'i mchog
yongs 'dzi dam pa mnyes phyir bdag gis bris
de las byung ba'i mgon tshogs rgya mtsho'i mthus
rgyal ba'i gsung la 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i sgras
mdo bstan zhung lugs phra zhi ba nyin byed 'od
sgrib gnyis kun bral dbung tshogs bcom byas nas
sku gsum go 'phang dam pa myur thob shog
